{"tid":30801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"輕鐵大叔","createTime":"2016-12-09T10:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T10:40:38.000Z","uid":61816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2994eadd02876d687029be03150af7b132384b1","tid":30801,"uid":61816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"今日搭輕鐵番屋企，一上到車就嘈到pk，不過我都遇咗架啦。d學生不斷講嘢，其他人又係，我都無為意，結果有個呀叔大叫：你班中學生一個二個都無d家教，係咁講講講，嘈Q住哂，識唔識尊重別人呀，而家d九十後成堆垃圾，正一社會敗類。<br />\n      講真，阿叔你咁樣叫法就好有禮貌，好有家教，好識尊重別人咩<br />\n<br />\n我當時有兩個方式應佢<br />\n1.我地有無家教關你差事咩，你算係老幾呀<br />\n2.係呀係呀，我地係咁架啦。不過d九十後米又係你地d人教出尼<br />\n<br />\n我最後只係同另一個fd講：受教了受教了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b1405681932c997f9e3ba94b738e54e15ea9b3","tid":30801,"uid":12791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"90 後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢度打火星文全部都係"},{"pid":"4de0c74fb7343d5df1e991da4155298cb9209da1","tid":30801,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"米你老母<br />\n尼你老母"},{"pid":"ece101f6a81acc95eb177957b4b38a339359ecd6","tid":30801,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"搭車最怕廢老同學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84123d773a2d06e0fb9b9df8737defbaace91bd8","tid":30801,"uid":61816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭車最怕廢老同學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我怕多BB車同輪椅"}]}